properties.abstract: An ascent through the landslide area of Goldau, with its matchlessly beautiful nature and wealth of rare orchids.
properties.description:
Starting in Goldau in the direction of Steinerberg, the road branches off to Spitzibel. While keeping the landslide area of Goldau in sight at al times, it climbs up to the Oberer Spizibel (upper Spizibel) alpine farm.

After a brief passage where you have to carry your bike and a single trail, you will reach Rufiberg. Thereafter, a long rapid descent to Lake Zug is guaranteed, then through cherry orchards in the valley back to the starting point.
properties.name: Arth-Goldau Tourismus
properties.title: Spitzibel Tour
